    <item>
      <title>红海动荡导致油价自 9 月以来首次月度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于红海船只袭击升级导致油轮交通转移，并引发人们对中东更广泛冲突的担忧，油价自 9 月以来首次月度上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 00:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冯托贝尔削减中国股票持有量以追逐其他地方的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/vontobel-curbs-chinese-stock-exposure-to-chase-growth-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冯托贝尔资产管理公司(Vontobel Asset Management)正在减持中国股票，以释放现金，购买巴西、印度和墨西哥等国更具吸引力的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/vontobel-curbs-chinese-stock-exposure-to-chase-growth-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
